---
---
<section data-test="comparison-section" style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-size:0.75rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Before / After</h2>
    <h3 style="font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--color-text);max-width:680px;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      The difference between a spec that drifts and one that doesn't.
    </h3>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5rem;">
      <div data-test="comparison-without" style="border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="padding:0.7rem 1rem;background:var(--color-surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;">Without RootSpec</div>
        <div style="padding:1.25rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.9rem;">
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">Requirements</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);">"The dashboard should show user data in a useful way. Make it look modern."</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">User Story</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);">"As a user I want to see my data so that I can make decisions."</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">Traceability</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text-muted);font-style:italic;">None. The story can't be traced to any decision.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">Validation</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text-muted);font-style:italic;">Manual QA, hope for the best, ship anyway.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-test="comparison-with" style="border:1px solid var(--color-accent);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="padding:0.7rem 1rem;background:var(--color-surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-accent);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;">With RootSpec</div>
        <div style="padding:1.25rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.9rem;">
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">L1 Design Pillar</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);">"Respects the user's time — show only what's actionable, hide what isn't."</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">L5 User Story</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);">"Given I am on the dashboard, When the page loads, Then I see only items requiring action."</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">Traceability</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);">Story → L3 Interaction → L2 Truth → L1 Pillar. Every decision auditable.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">Validation</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);">Automated Cypress test. Story passes or it doesn't. No ambiguity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
